text: Keala is a given name of Hawaiian origin. Notable people with the given name include: *Keala Keanaaina (born 1976), American football player *Keala Kennelly (born 1977), American surfer *Leonard Keala Kwan, (1931-2000), slack- key guitar performer who recorded in the 1950s-1960s. *Keala O'Sullivan (born 1950), American diver *Keala Settle (born 1975), American singer
